*  2006   &ndash; [[Frank Stanton (executive)|Frank Stanton]], American businessman (b. 1908)
*[[2007]] &ndash; [[Nicholas Pumfrey]], English judge (b. 1951)
*  2007   &ndash; [[Akbar Radi]], Iranian playwright (b. 1939)
*[[2008]] &ndash; [[Harold Pinter]], English scriptwriter, director, and actor, [[Nobel Prize in Literature|Nobel Prize]] laureate (b. 1930)
*[[2009]] &ndash; [[Marcus Bakker]], Dutch politician (b. 1923)
*  2009   &ndash; [[Rafael Caldera]],  Venezuelan lawyer and politician, 65th [[President of Venezuela]] (b. 1916)
*  2009   &ndash; [[George Michael (sportscaster)|George Michael]], American sportscaster (b. 1939)
